										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>13 Excelentes Estratégias de </strong><strong><em>Marketing </em></strong><strong>para </strong><strong><em>E-Commerce</em></strong><strong> em 2020</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


