<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>Outra maneira de incentivar os visitantes a concluir a compra é oferecer brindes com o checkout.</p>



<p>Assim como o frete grátis, amostras grátis ou upgrades também podem aumentar o valor médio do pedido e a receita das vendas.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.esteelauder.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Estée Lauder</a> oferece várias opções de amostras <em>deluxe</em> durante o checkout:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="854" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-1024x854.png" alt="Estee Lauder Checkout Free Sample" class="wp-image-92909" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-1024x854.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-300x250.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-768x640.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-380x317.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-600x500.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-760x634.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-588x490.png 588w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-220x183.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample-385x321.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Estee-Lauder-Checkout-Free-Sample.png 1065w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Além de incentivar o visitante a concluir a compra, eles oferecem uma amostra adicional se o usuário gastar mais $8 no site.</p>



<p>O uso de amostras grátis como ferramenta de <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/upselling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">upselling</a> é brilhante.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Leitura adicional</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







